OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK charities call for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmenstrual leave for severe 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpain                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK charities have called on the        
OL,6, government to bring in leave for those 
OL,7, who suffer from menstrual pain.        
OL,9,FIt comes as Spanish politicians approve
OL,10,Fa new draft bill that would allow those
OL,11,Fwith painful periods to have three days
OL,12,Foff a month.                           
OL,14,FCurrent UK employment law states       
OL,15,Fworkers should use sick leave if they  
OL,16,Fneed time off work.                    
OL,18,FEmma Cox from Endometriosis UK says:   
OL,19,F"We need to challenge the squeamishness
OL,20,Fand silence around menstrual health".  
